		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001117_0001"/><!--pb/@n='20r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right">London 24<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> Oct</p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>1857</p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear Sir</p>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="words"/>As a deputation 
<lb/>from the British Association 
<lb/>is to have an interview 
<lb/>with <persName>Lord Clarendon</persName>
<lb/>next week on the subject 
<lb/>of granting a vessel 
<lb/>to survey the <placeName>Zambesi</placeName>
<lb/>it would strengthen their 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001117_0002"/><!--pb/@n='20v'--> 
<lb/>hands if your chamber 
<lb/>of commerce would 
<lb/>present their resolution 
<lb/>(if any) in favour 
<lb/>of developing the 
<lb/>resources of Africa  
<lb/>during that time<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>Perhaps you have 
<lb/>already presented it. 
<lb/><choice><reg>I</reg><orig>i</orig></choice>f so you will excuse 
<lb/>this hint<reg>.</reg></p>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001117_0003"/><!--pb/@n='21r'-->
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">I am Dear Sir</p>
<lb/><p>Truly yours</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">David Livingstone</p>
<lb/>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">Thomas Milne Esq</p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">Most kind salutations 
<lb/>to <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> M.</persName></p>
			
</div>
